{"title":"悼伟人","authors":["莫文骅"],"dates":[{"year":1989,"month":4,"day":27}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"悼伟人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"莫文骅"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天资聪敏学艰辛，卓绝才华冠群英。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"勇拒逆流冲恶浪，肩挑五岳自忘身。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"直率诚实无韬晦，胸怀豁达语贴心。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正需鼎力撑大厦，痛君长逝泪盈衿！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"１９８９年４月２０日"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}